{
  "stem": "13469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we went to Switzerland-- Lake Lucerne.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It, it was my parents, Ruti, and me, the four of us, really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to the Black Forest and those kinds of places.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And life was really very nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And eventually, I also went to school in Berlin, to a normal state school, not very far from where we lived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember those things because I have the actual reports, the school reports, from those days.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they help to remind me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I actually have a photograph in the class that I attended in 1935 in the state school in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very much, except that I did pretty well at school, from what I can see from the reports.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't remember, for example, having any other Jewish classmates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, I don't remember anything about Judaism from those days at all, which is rather interesting, in that I have amongst all those documents a report from a Jewish community school that I attended presumably on Sundays, and where I did get a religious instruction.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I don't remember anything about that at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, obviously, it must have happened, because I've got the report.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then my name's is on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I must have done it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But whether I've blocked out [LAUGHS] all my Jewish connections from those early days, I don't believe so.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I just don't remember anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember ever having gone to a synagogue in Berlin, or having Friday night services at home in Berlin, Although, we may have done it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I, I found out all sorts of things later on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I just can't remember any of those sort of things from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What, what we do remember is, of course, that we had the rise of the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
